tags: Value for money,Wait time,
review: I had very bad experience at Dr Swapna's clinic. I had booked the appointment through Practo for 4:30 pm. The doctor did not show up till 5:30 pm. And only when my turn was about to come, the receptionist told me that the consultation fee is more than what is mentioned on Practo. On Practo it is mentioned 800, but she was asking me to pay 1000 as it was a public holiday. She told that they charge 1000 rs on holidays and Sundays which is a very bad excuse for charging extra money. My husband and I immediately left the clinic without seeing the doctor. Soon after 5 minutes, the receptionist started calling me that I can go back and pay only 8 and see the doctor. She kept on calling 4-5 times, but I didn't go back. I definitely do not recommend this clinic.
